sequenceDiagram
    participant vLLM as vLLM Pod<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ
    participant ZMQ as ZMQ SUB Pool<br/>(kvevents.Pool)<br/>FNV-1a sharded
    participant Adapter as Engine Adapter<br/>(vLLM/SGLang)
    participant TokenProc as Token Processor<br/>(FNV-64a CBOR)
    participant Index as Block Index<br/>(LRU/Ristretto/Redis)
    participant UDS as UDS Tokenizer<br/>UDS gRPC Sidecar
    participant EPP as llm-d EPP<br/>(Inference Scheduler)
    participant Scorer as Block Scorer
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Shared Storage<br/>(PVC / S3)

    Note over vLLM,Index: Flow 1: KV-Event Ingestion (Write Path)
    vLLM->>ZMQ: BlockStored / BlockRemoved<br/>ZMQ PUB 5557/TCP (msgpack)
    ZMQ->>Adapter: Route to shard worker<br/>(FNV-1a hash of pod ID)
    Adapter->>TokenProc: Parse event, extract tokens
    TokenProc->>Index: Update block residency<br/>(in-process or Redis 6379/TCP)

    Note over EPP,Scorer: Flow 2: Pod Scoring (Read Path)
    EPP->>EPP: Receive inference request
    EPP->>UDS: Tokenize prompt<br/>gRPC over UDS
    UDS->>UDS: Apply chat template<br/>(vLLM renderer)
    UDS-->>EPP: Token IDs + offsets
    EPP->>TokenProc: Hash token blocks<br/>(chained FNV-64a over CBOR)
    TokenProc->>Index: Lookup block residency<br/>(per-pod cache hits)
    Index-->>TokenProc: Block locations per pod
    TokenProc->>Scorer: Score pods by prefix match
    Scorer-->>EPP: Ranked pod list<br/>(cache-hit scores)

    Note over UDS,HF: Flow 3: Tokenizer Initialization
    UDS->>HF: Download tokenizer model<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Bearer HF_TOKEN
    HF-->>UDS: Tokenizer files
    UDS->>UDS: InitializeTokenizer<br/>(load model + renderer)

    Note over vLLM,FS: Flow 4: KV-Cache Offloading (fs-backend)
    vLLM->>vLLM: KV blocks in GPU memory
    vLLM->>FS: Offload blocks<br/>POSIX I/O / GDS / NIXL S3<br/>(hash-partitioned directories)
    FS-->>vLLM: Load cached blocks<br/>(content-addressable lookup)
